Data availability

            All public data supporting this study are available via Zenodo at https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.19628489 (ref. 62). Climate data were obtained from the ER56A5 Land dataset (ECMWF/ERA5_LAND/DAILY_AGGR at Google Earth Engine); NDVI data from the National Tibetan Plateau Data Center (https://developers.google.com/earth-engine/datasets/catalog/ECMWF_ERA5_LAND_DAILY_AGGR); and maize phenology data from ref. 54. Socioeconomic, agricultural production and policy data contain confidential information and are available from the first author on reasonable request. Source data are provided with this paper.
          Code availability

            All regression and figure codes in R and Stata used in this study are available via Zenodo at https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.19628489 (ref. 62).
